ea, feel free to comment.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify\">art by @hoshi_sama2 and @BS_artsss on twitter</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">── <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b2735ab6-c130-414e-825f-05df0dcd754f_character-%EA%A3%91%E0%AD%A7-%D6%B9-request-box\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 186, 212)\">requests</span></a> ⸝⸝ <a href=\"https://pin.it/1MdurbvCu\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 186, 212)\">where I get most of my images from</span></a> !</p><h6 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)\">caitlyn, caitlyn kiramman, caitvi, vi, violet, arcane</span></h6>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"n8KBE1WJTkPhj4WK3Oxw8.webp","creator":"faeriebleu","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧛 Vampire","👭 Multiple","⛓️ Dominant","👩‍❤️‍👩 WLW","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","👩 FemPov"],"chats":1783,"messages":43054,"created_at":"2025-05-19T15:12:13.944447+00:00"}